# Railway GitHub integracija

Projekt koristi Railway Continuous Deployment mehanizam.

Proces deploymenta:

```text
Developer
    |
    v
Git Push
    |
    v
GitHub Repository
    |
    v
GitHub Actions
(Build + Test)
    |
    v
Railway GitHub Integration
    |
    v
Automatic Deployment
```

Svaka promjena na `main` grani automatski prolazi kroz ovaj proces.

